<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
    <!-- EN: Azzy's Weapon Library -->
  <AWL_Mod>Azzy的武器库</AWL_Mod>

    <!-- EN: Reset to default -->
  <Reset>重置为默认</Reset>

    <!-- EN: Use ammunition system -->
  <EnableAmmoSystem>使用弹药系统</EnableAmmoSystem>
    <!-- EN: When checked, the ammunition system is enabled. -->
  <EnableTheAmmoSystem>当勾选时，启用弹药系统。</EnableTheAmmoSystem>

    <!-- EN: Use the backup ammunition system -->
  <EnableBackupAmmoSystemLabel>使用备用弹药系统</EnableBackupAmmoSystemLabel>
    <!-- EN: When checked, some weapons will need to be loaded by resources. -->
  <EnableBackupAmmoSystemDesc>当勾选时，部分武器将会需要装填。</EnableBackupAmmoSystemDesc>

    <!-- EN: Global multiplier for backup ammo capacity -->
  <BackupAmmoMultipilerLabel>备用弹药上限全局乘数</BackupAmmoMultipilerLabel>
    <!-- EN: The backup ammo capacity limit of all weapons using the backup ammo system will be multiplied by this value. -->
  <BackupAmmoMultipilerDesc>所有使用备用弹药系统的武器的备弹上限均会乘以这个值。</BackupAmmoMultipilerDesc>

    <!-- EN: Ammunition gizmo is displayed only when a pawn is selected -->
  <OnlyShowAmmoGizmoWhenSelectedOneThingLabel>仅在选择一个殖民者时显示弹药数据</OnlyShowAmmoGizmoWhenSelectedOneThingLabel>
    <!-- EN: Ammunition gizmo is displayed only when a pawn is selected. -->
  <OnlyShowAmmoGizmoWhenSelectedOneThingDesc>仅在选择一个殖民者时显示弹药数据。</OnlyShowAmmoGizmoWhenSelectedOneThingDesc>

    <!-- EN: Non-player controled pawn randomly switch weapon modes -->
  <RandomWeaponModeForNonPlayerPawnLabel>非玩家单位随机切换武器模式</RandomWeaponModeForNonPlayerPawnLabel>
    <!-- EN: After activation, if a controled pawn is equipped with weapons of multiple modes, it will automatically switch to one of the modes.\n\nWhen turned off, only the default mode is used. -->
  <RandomWeaponModeForNonPlayerPawnDesc>启用后，如果非玩家单位装备了具有多个模式的武器，将会自动切换至其中一种模式。\n\n关闭则仅使用默认模式。</RandomWeaponModeForNonPlayerPawnDesc>

</LanguageData>